agrees to my terms,

00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:25.240
I'll let you go.

00:04:30.759 --> 00:04:31.600
Sir…

00:04:32.040 --> 00:04:34.759
Who says the Governor's Residence
can't carry the Ruan name?

00:04:45.839 --> 00:04:47.439
My daughter, Ruan Feifei,

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.720
was burned alive.

00:04:52.399 --> 00:04:54.000
Then, I found you.

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:56.800
I wanted to turn you into Ruan Feifei

00:04:57.199 --> 00:04:59.120
to avenge the Ruan family.

00:05:06.279 --> 00:05:08.199
Huo Beishan's real daughter

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:09.920
wiped out the entire Huo family.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:12.120
That's true revenge!

00:05:12.519 --> 00:05:14.000
This is revenge at its finest!

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:21.319
Now,

00:05:22.360 --> 00:05:23.879
