00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.600
on the path to the afterlife.

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:33.360
The Huo family
may have lost their power,

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:34.959
but we did hold

00:05:35.720 --> 00:05:36.959
an engagement banquet.

00:05:38.959 --> 00:05:41.079
Qingwan belongs to the Sheng family.

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:43.639
You can't touch her.

00:05:49.879 --> 00:05:50.600
I told you,

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:54.879
I'll be your weapon no matter

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:58.720
who your enemies are.

00:06:04.399 --> 00:06:05.199
What's this?

00:06:06.600 --> 00:06:07.879
You want to kill me?

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.439
Don't forget.

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:11.959
It was the Huo family

00:06:11.959 --> 00:06:13.519
who destroyed the Ruan family first!

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.600
Besides,

00:06:16.839 --> 00:06:19.079
I raised you for 15 years.

00:06:35.879 --> 00:06:36.720
