00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:09.160
I'm going to find Huo Xiu.

00:07:10.260 --> 00:07:11.439
Why do you still want to go after him?

00:07:11.639 --> 00:07:12.879
He killed your real parents.

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:14.200
He destroyed the entire Huo family!

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:15.319
I'm not Huo Qingwan.

00:07:16.199 --> 00:07:17.319
I'm not Huo Qingwan!

00:07:18.439 --> 00:07:19.920
I'm not!

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:23.439
Even if you don't believe it,

00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:26.040
